OL,4,C'interlocutor' slammed by Justice
OL,5,CMinister
OL,7,FThe appointment of an "interlocutor"
OL,8,Fto examine whether a formal process of
OL,9,Fengagement with paramilitary groups in
OL,10,FNorthern Ireland is required to bring
OL,11,Fabout their disbandment risks
OL,12,Fundermining work done to tackle
OL,13,Forganised crime, Stormont Justice
OL,14,FMinister Naomi Long has said.
OL,16,FNorthern Ireland Secretary Hilary Benn
OL,17,Fhas announced that Fleur Ravensbergen
OL,18,Fwill take up the role of Independent
OL,19,FExpert on paramilitary group
OL,20,Ftransition to disbandment.
OL,26,@oD@WOUoD@dO]
