OL,7,FMs Ravensbergen is a conflict
OL,8,Fresolution and negotiation
OL,9,Fpractitioner and a lecturer in
OL,10,Fconflict resolution and governance at
OL,11,Fthe University of Amsterdam.
OL,13,FThe appointment has been made jointly
OL,14,Fwith Jim O'Callaghan, the Irish
OL,15,FMinister for Justice, Home Affairs and
OL,16,FMigration.
