OL,7,FMaking the announcement, Northern
OL,8,FIreland Secretary Hilary Benn said it
OL,9,Fwas right that the governments "test
OL,10,Fwhether there is more that can be done
OL,11,Fto end paramilitarism".
OL,13,FThe two governments committed to
OL,14,Fmaking the appointment earlier this
OL,15,Fyear following a recommendation from
OL,16,Fthe Independent Reporting Commission
OL,17,F(IRC) that a "twin track" process of
OL,18,Flaw enforcement and tackling the roots
OL,19,Fof paramilitarism is needed.
