OL,5,CMinister
OL,7,FMr Benn said: "The Government is
OL,8,Fcommitted to working with partners in
OL,9,FNorthern Ireland to support efforts
OL,10,Fagainst the enduring threats and harms
OL,11,Fposed to communities by paramilitary
OL,12,Fgroups.
OL,14,F"There is no justification for
OL,15,Fparamilitary groups and they should
OL,16,Fhave left the stage long ago.
OL,18,F"But they haven't. It's therefore
OL,19,Fright that we test whether there is
OL,20,Fmore that can be done to end
OL,21,Fparamilitarism."
OL,26,@oD@OOUvD@AOUzD@AOU}D@PO]
