OL,5,CMinister
OL,7,FHe added: "This appointment follows
OL,8,Fthe commitment made by the UK
OL,9,FGovernment and the Government of
OL,10,FIreland to commission a short scoping
OL,11,Fand engagement exercise to assess
OL,12,Fwhether there is merit in, and support
OL,13,Ffor, a formal process of engagement to
OL,14,Fbring about paramilitary group
OL,15,Ftransition to disbandment."
OL,17,FBut Alliance Party leader Ms Long said
OL,18,Fparamilitary groups should already
OL,19,Fhave disbanded.
OL,26,@oD@KOUwD@[O]
