OL,3,CAppointment of paramilitary
OL,4,C'interlocutor' slammed by Justice
OL,5,CMinister
OL,7,F"The idea that paramilitary groups can
OL,8,Ftransition into law-abiding entities
OL,9,Fhas long since moved beyond the point
OL,10,Fof credibility.
OL,12,F"They cannot continue to be treated as
OL,13,Fif they are genuinely committed to
OL,14,Freform ` that moment passed long ago."
OL,16,FShe added: "Whilst we all want to see
OL,17,Fparamilitarism ended and those
OL,18,Fcurrently engaged in it to desist, I
OL,19,Fcannot understand what the impediment
OL,20,Fis to them doing so now, if they are
OL,21,Fgenuinely keen to do so.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUvD@fO]xD@LOU
