OL,3,CAppointment of paramilitary
OL,4,C'interlocutor' slammed by Justice
OL,5,CMinister
OL,7,F"There can be no negotiation or
OL,8,Fsweeteners involved, so it is
OL,9,Fdifficult to see what purpose an
OL,10,Finterlocutor will serve, but easy to
OL,11,Fsee how it could give these groups a
OL,12,Fcredibility which they don't deserve."
OL,14,FMs Ravensbergen will take up the role
OL,15,Fwithin the existing IRC and is
OL,16,Fexpected to complete the scoping and
OL,17,Fengagement exercise and submit a
OL,18,Freport by August 2026.
OL,20,FThe appointment will be for a period
OL,21,Fof one year.
